<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a202c; /* Dark background */
            color: #e2e8f0; /* Light text */
            display: flex; /* Use flexbox for centering */
            justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */
            align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
            min-height: 100vh; /* Full viewport height */
        }
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #2d3748; /* Darker gray background for content */
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-red-500 mb-4">404</h1>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Página No Encontrada</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">Lo sentimos, la página que buscas no existe.</p>
        <a href="/" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-md shadow-lg transition duration-200">Volver al Inicio</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>